Package edu.xtec.jclic.automation

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ActiveBagContentKit.Compatible
    Activities should implement this interface when its contents are formed basically by ActiveBagContent objects, in order to let AutoContentProvider objects to check whether they are compatible with them.
    TextActivityContentKit.Compatible
    Activities should implement this interface if based on TextActivityDocument objects, in order to let AutoContentProvider objects to check whether they are compatible with them.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ActiveBagContentKit
    This class is used by Activity objects to interact with AutoContentProvider objects.
    AutoContentProvider
    This abstract class is the base for all the classes that provide contents to JClic activities, usually based on random values.
    AutoContentProviderEditor  
    TextActivityContentKit
